'''Amdal aserɣin''' neɣ '''Amdal aɛrab''' (s [[Taɛrabt|Tserɣint:  ''الوطن العربي'' , ''al-waṭan al-ʿarabī'') d irem arakal-aserti yettwafken i yiwet n temnaṭ yezdin deg [[amezruy|umezruy]] d [[idles|yidles]] d [[tutlayt]], Amdal aserɣin d tamnaṭ yeddan seg [[agaraw Aṭlasi|ugaraw anaṭlas]] deg umalu ar [[ilel aɛrab|yilel aserɣin]] d [[abagu Afarsi|ubagu n Faris]] deg usamar, s wakka yezdi yakk [[awanak|timura]] yellan d igmanen deg [[tamɣunt Taserɣint|temɣunt Taserɣint]] deg [[Amalu n Asya|umalu n Asya]] d [[Tafriqt n Ugafa|Tefrikt n ugafa]] d usamar-is, Amdal aserɣin d win yettawin daɣen kra n tamiwin yettwaṭṭfen am seg kra n tmura ur nelli ara d tiserɣinin am [[Falesṭin (Tamnaḍt)|Falestin]] d [[Agni n Gulan|ugni n Gulan]] d [[Senjaq n Alexandrit]] d tamiwin tigafanin n Surya id tefka [[Fransa]] i [[Turkya]] d [[Tigzirin Tiknariyin]] d [[Sebta]] d [[Mlilt]] d [[Tagzirt n iceffaren|tegzirt n iceffaren]] (yettwaṭṭfen s ɣur [[Spanya]]) d [[Ahwaz]] d kra n tegzirin n Emarat yettwaṭṭfen sɣur [[Iran]]

